            <label>2</label>
            <p>These data were provided by Dougan’s group at the Wellcome Trust Sanger Institute and could be obtained from <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://www.sanger.ac.uk/resources/downloads/bacteria/salmonella.html">http://www.sanger.ac.uk/resources/downloads/bacteria/salmonella.html</ext-link>.</p>
