          <caption>
            <title>CRISPR sizing by PCR for the rapid comparison of <italic>Salmonella</italic> spp isolates.</title>
            <p>Results of PCR amplification for 8 <italic>S. enterica</italic> serotype Typhimurium isolates collected from the same city during a single week (cluster E in <xref ref-type="supplementary-material" rid="pone.0036995.s009">Table S7</xref>). Three cases were from the same food poisoning cluster (the food isolate was also tested), whereas the other cases were unrelated.</p>
